news.title: Elon Musk To Ditch Tesla Gigafactory In Mexico After Trump's Win? Economy Minister Wants 'A Meeting' - Tesla  ( NASDAQ:TSLA )
news.content: Donald Trump's winning the 2024 presidential election is expected to have a negative impact on the electric vehicle sector. Tesla Inc TSLA could benefit from CEO Elon Musk's close relationship with the president-elect. However, the company's plan to build a Gigafactory in Mexico could be at stake.

news.title: Sony Posts Upbeat Earnings, Joins Tesla, Upstart, Doximity, Fortrea, Axon Enterprise And Other Big Stocks Moving Higher On Friday - Sony Gr  ( NYSE:SONY )
news.content: U.S. stocks were higher, with the Dow Jones index gaining more than 200 points on Friday. Shares of Sony Group Corporation SONY rose sharply during Thursday's session after reporting better-than-expected second-quarter earnings and raising FY24 revenue outlook.
